    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single below-level factor (Test conditions, achieved 1 vs required 2) is offset by the strong multi-laboratory experimental dataset (N=11), tight QoI agreement across all three metrics, and the conservative nature of the single test condition relative to in vivo loading. The FEA ensemble is judged credible for the stated COU at Medium assurance level.",
